content.rendered:
Directed by Samir Soni

Written by Vrushali Telang

Cast Nora Fatehi (Sandy).Elena Kazan. Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Suparna Moitra (Aanchal (as Suparna Krishna)). Pitobash (Percy).Sameer Sharma. Zenia Starr (Ritu). Sanjay Suri (Rajeev)

Languages Hindi

Producers Manoj Kumar. Vinay Kumar. Devika Tandon Nair. Samir Soni. Ambika Suri. Sanjay Suri

Production KAHWA Entertainment. Studio Unee
